quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,O woondirii kammu e hoodere fuɗoore jemma
  86,2,Hol ko anndin ma ko woni hoodere feeñoore jemma
  86,3,Hoodere fooynunde
  86,4,Alah fittaandu si wonah ina e dow mayru deenoowo
  86,5,Yo aade ndaaru ko o tagraa ko
  86,6,O tagiraama ko e ndiyam nduñotoɗam
  86,7,Hombo e hakkunde keeci gorko e ƴi*e ɓernde debba
  86,8,Hombo hattani ruttude mbo
  86,9,ñande cuuɗiiɗi kuncaa
  86,10,Alanah mbo semmbe wonah balloowo
  86,11,Mi woondirii kammu jom ɗate ngun
  86,12,O woondirii leydi mbaɗndi petti
  86,13,Pellet o Quraana kombo ceerndoowol
  86,14,Mbo wonah gaajaate
  86,15,Pellet kamɓe hoɓe pewja peeje
  86,16,Mi fewja feere
  86,17,Muñanɓe muñangol setta